cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or the associated research data, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "GEO Multi-Vertical Citation Tracker"
abstract: >-
  Longitudinal empirical study pipeline tracking citation patterns of 69
  Brazilian entities (61 real + 8 fictional controls) across 4 verticals
  (fintech, retail, healthcare, technology) by 5 LLMs (GPT-4o-mini,
  Claude Haiku 4.5, Gemini 2.5 Pro, Perplexity Sonar, Groq Llama 3.3 70B).
  Target 90-day observation window · ~25,920 observations. Companion to
  the practitioner paper "Algorithmic Authority" (SSRN DOI
  10.2139/ssrn.6460680 · Zenodo DOI 10.5281/zenodo.19687866).
